# Title

ADR-0001 Usage of a automation tool for the CI/CD Tasks

## Status

Accepted (4/0)

## Context

To make rapid development possible we are considering using a tool to make our lives easier.

## Decision

After a short discussion we decided on using GitHub actions for our CI/CD Tasks.

## Consequences

CI/CD Tasks need to be automated and maintaned using GitHub Actions. We need to strengthen our knowledge on the usage of this tool and make sure that these actions are properly mainted and hardend against possible attack vectors
